      "content": "i hear that, but what about the perspective that the ruling itself was politically motivated by western interests to contain china? if they don't recognize the court, does that mean their position is just fundamentally wrong, or is there a legitimate debate about the authority of these international bodies in these huge geopolitical disputes?",
